<p><a name="As_writer.2Fartist" id="As_writer.2Fartist"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Frank_Miller_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: As writer/artist">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">As writer/artist</span></h3>
