<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Frank_Miller.jpg" class="image" title="Miller at the 1982 Comic-Con"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/71/Frank_Miller.jpg/180px-Frank_Miller.jpg" width="180" height="272" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
