<p><a name="Awards" id="Awards"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Frank_Miller_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Awards">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Awards</span></h2>
<p><b>Eisner Awards</b></p>
<p>Best Short Story - 1995</p>
<p>Best Finite Series/Limited Series - 1991, 1995, 1996, 1999</p>
<p>Best Graphic Album: New - 1991</p>
<p>Best Graphic Album: Reprint - 1993, 1998</p>
<p>Best Writer/Artist - 1991, 1993, 1999</p>
<p>Best Artist/Penciller/Inker or Penciller/Inker Team - 1993</p>
<p><b>Kirby Awards</b></p>
<p>Best Single Issue - 1986, 1987</p>
<p>Best Graphic Album, 1987</p>
<p>Best Writer/Artist (single or team) - 1986</p>
<p>Best Art Team - 1987</p>
<p><b>Harvey Awards</b></p>
<p>Best Continuing or Limited Series - 1996, 1999</p>
<p>Best Graphic Album of Original Work - 1998</p>
<p>Best Domestic Reprint Project - 1997</p>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Cannes_Film_Festival" title="Cannes Film Festival">Cannes Film Festival</a></b></p>
<p><a href="/wiki/Palme_D%27Or" title="Palme D'Or" class="mw-redirect">Palme D'Or</a> - 2005 (nominated)</p>
